Manga
Written and illustrated by Sigma Torai, My Matchmaking Partner Is My Student and a Troublemaker was serialized on Screamo's ComicFesta service from November 15, 2015, to March 17, 2019. Its chapters were compiled by Seiunsha into five tankōbon volumes released from September 18, 2016, to June 18, 2019.
